Now let me use the terminal to force close Firefox:
Great, now let me take another screenshot to see the desktop without Firefox:
Now I see the Firefox icon on the taskbar. Let me click it to launch Firefox:

Great! Firefox has launched successfully and is working properly. We can see that it loads and displays web pages correctly. The browser appears to be Firefox-ESR as expected, and all basic functionality seems to be working normally.
